# Code Style Rules
- New components must be under 300 lines. If a component grows beyond 300 lines, split it.
- Extract reusable UI elements (cards, modals, badges) into components/common/
- No inline styles for new code — use Tailwind classes only
- Every new function must have a one-line JSDoc comment
- Keep imports organized: React first, then external libs, then internal modules
- Use the existing logger utility (utils/logger.ts) instead of console.log
